6 An Act relating to Commercial Pet Breeders and Animal
Shelter Licensing Act; amending 4 O.S. 2021, Section
7 30.8, which relates to expiration and renewal of
license; extending time for renewal; requiring the
8 Oklahoma Department of Agriculture, Food, and
Forestry to provide certain platform; and providing
9 an effective date.
10
