12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 4 O.S. 2021, Section 30.8, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 30.8. A. An animal shelter operator or commercial pet
16 breeder who is not in violation of the Commercial Pet Breeders and
17 Animal Shelter Licensing Act or any rule adopted under the
18 Commercial Pet Breeders and Animal Shelter Licensing Act may renew
19 the license of the person by:
20 1. Submitting a renewal application to the Oklahoma Department
21 of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry on the form prescribed by the
22 Department;
23 2. Complying with any other renewal requirements adopted by the
24 Department; and
SENATE FLOOR VERSION - SB1082 SFLR Page 1
